Wylie Lineage Name: dwags lha sgam po gdan rabs
ri bo dge 'phel gdan sa pa
sde dge dgon chen gdan rabs
rgyal lha khang gdan sa ba
chab mdo byams pa gling gdan rabs
dwags po grwa tshang gi mkhan thog
dmu dge bkra shis 'khor lo khri
rnga yul sgo mang mkhan rabs
rong po dgon chen gdan rabs
d+hi tsha bkra shis chos sding khri
a mchog dga' ldan chos 'khor gling khri
a mchog mtshan nyid dgon gyi gdan rabs
sa skya rin chen sgang bla brang gdung rabs
